Features and Enhancements

NBO Adequacy
  • Initial implementation of Adequacy
    • View, Add, Edit and Delete an Adequacy Analysis
    • View results for an Adequacy Analysis
    • Export an Adequacy Analysis to CSV
    • Import a Population file to use in Adequacy Analysis

Issues Fixed

Competitive Access in NBO
  • Fixed an issue where Network Models "In Progress" can be selected in Competitive Access
